    "description": "Grow your career with Equitas Small Finance Bank Ventures Solutions! We are hiring a Risk Analyst for our Pune team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Equitas Small Finance Bank Ventures Solutions:\nEquitas Small Finance Bank Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Equitas Small Finance Bank Ventures Solutions!",
